Project description

Team and repository tags

oslo.cache

oslo.cache aims to provide a generic caching mechanism for OpenStack projectsby wrapping the dogpile.cache library. The dogpile.cachelibrary provides support memoization, key value storage and interfaces to commoncaching backends such as Memcached.

  • Free software: Apache license

  • Documentation: https://docs.openstack.org/oslo.cache/latest/

  • Source: https://opendev.org/openstack/oslo.cache/

  • Bugs: https://bugs.launchpad.net/oslo.cache

  • Release notes: https://docs.openstack.org/releasenotes/oslo.cache/
